### Signup
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ada Lovelace",
  "email": "ada@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ada@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get ideas
GET http://localhost:5000/api/ideas

### Submit startup idea
POST http://localhost:5000/api/ideas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "AI bookkeeping assistant",
  "description": "A web app that helps local stores track sales and expenses.",
  "targetAudience": "Small business owners",
  "budget": 5000,
  "experienceLevel": "Beginner"
}

### Get saved roadmaps
GET http://localhost:5000/api/roadmaps

### Generate startup roadmap
POST http://localhost:5000/generate-roadmap
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ideaId": "idea-123",
  "title": "AI bookkeeping assistant",
  "description": "A web app that helps local stores track sales and expenses.",
  "targetAudience": "Small business owners",
  "budget": 5000,
  "experienceLevel": "Beginner"
}

### Generate startup ideas
POST http://localhost:5000/generate-ideas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "education"
}

### Startup mentor chat
POST http://localhost:5000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ideaId": "idea-123",
  "title": "AI bookkeeping assistant",
  "description": "A web app that helps local stores track sales and expenses.",
  "targetAudience": "Small business owners",
  "budget": 5000,
  "experienceLevel": "Beginner",
  "question": "What should my MVP include?",
  "history": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "How do I validate demand?"
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Start with 10 interviews and a simple landing page test."
    }
  ]
}

### Generate startup roadmap from plain idea text
POST http://localhost:5000/generate-roadmap
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idea": "Build a subscription-based app that helps remote teams run daily standups asynchronously."
}

### Get current user
GET http://localhost:5000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Protected route
GET http://localhost:5000/api/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
